modules.description: This module manages console capabilities for terminal features like ANSI color, UTF-8 output, and virtual terminal control sequences. It provides functions to create console instances with or without virtual terminal support and query their capabilities. Use cases include enabling colored output conditionally, detecting terminal compatibility, and handling Unicode display correctly.

This module handles terminal features such as ANSI color, UTF-8 output, and virtual terminal control sequences. It allows creating console instances with optional virtual terminal support and querying their capabilities. Use it to enable conditional colored output, detect terminal compatibility, and ensure correct Unicode display.
